### getSlice() {#a75a54304c99ee264027c946c229d2ab6}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>ArrayRef&lt; Instruction &#42; &gt; llvm::sandboxir::SeedBundle::getSlice (unsigned StartIdx, unsigned MaxVecRegBits, bool ForcePowOf2)</>}>
\\Returns a slice of seed elements, starting at the element <code>StartIdx</code>, with a total size &lt;= <code>MaxVecRegBits</code>, or an empty slice if the requirements cannot be met .

If <code>ForcePowOf2</code> is true, then the returned slice will have a total number of bits that is a power of 2.
